high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the black shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Pick up the rightmost apple off of the black shelving unit.
Turn around and walk towards the black table, then hang a left and walk up to the stove and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the apple inside, then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave, take out the apple, and close the microwave door.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the black shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Put the heated apple on top of the black shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on top of a black shelving unit.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the small black table.
Pick the apple on the right up.
Turn around and then go left to face the microwave above the stove.
Put the apple in the microwave and turn it on and then take the apple out and shut the door.
Turn around and cross the room and turn right to stand in front of the black table in the corner.
Put the apple down on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed apple on a table.

high_descs: Turn to the left, walk to the black table.
Pick up the apple to the right of the spatula.
Turn around, walk to the stove.
Place the apple in the microwave above the stove, heat up the apple for a few seconds, take out the apple.
Turn around, walk to the black table by the white table.
Place the apple to the right of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated up apple on the black table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the square table with knife  on top of it.
Pick up the apple from the square table.
Turn around, walk to the round table, turn left, walk to the oven
Put the apple in the oven, wait 2 seconds, take the apple out of the oven
Turn around and walk to the door
Turn right, put the apple back onto the square table.
anns.task_desc: Warm the apple up in the oven , put it back on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk towards the black table.
Pick up the apple on the right side.
Turn around, walk towards the circle table, turn left towards the stove.
Place the apple into the microwave to heat it and then take it out.
Turn around, walk towards the door, make a right towards the black table.
Place the apple back onto the table to the left of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Heat one of the apples from the black table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the black table.
Pick up the rightmost apple.
Turn around and veer left to the stove and microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave. Place it to the left of the mug.
Turn around and walk to the right to the original black table.
Put the apple approximately where it first was on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on a table.
